A roommate deals with
the rental contract

161
00:05:44.820 --> 00:05:46.874
on your behalf and
you pay them in cash

162
00:05:47.529 --> 00:05:50.060
A friend sends a
bank transfer for you

163
00:05:50.510 --> 00:05:52.111
A local store allows you to

164
00:05:52.113 --> 00:05:53.392
pickup mail there

165
